{"tid":839150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國男在迦納隨地大便　被民眾發現結果...","createTime":"2018-09-27T16:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T05:15:54.000Z","uid":184679,"like":324,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"15bd8495721f59505fca3e51a6c0720578bf444a","tid":839150,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T16:53:35.000Z","msg":"一名中國籍男子，在一處花園裡大便，迦納當地民眾發現後，要求他收拾他拉的大便。<br />\n據奈及利亞《pulse》報導，instablog9ja在社群媒體《Instagram》上分享影片，指出一名居住在迦納當地的中國男子，跑到一處花園裏面大便，一群民眾發現後拿起手機錄影圍上，中國男子也出聲道歉。而民眾也拿出一把鏟子遞給他，要求他收拾好剛拉出來的大便。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180928/1437716/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180928%2F1437716%2F&d=%2BoX3ALZ8q%2FvQFAm0m5BtCG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=d8a3de42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180928%2F1437716%2F&h=f29e2e7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180928/1437716/</a>"},{"pid":"429bc12e85ec3e143d21e659e33098c236046c9c","tid":839150,"uid":38100,"like":388,"dislike":1,"score":387,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:06:01.000Z","msg":"乜咁好心啊 提供埋個剷比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7606f958423cbf96d49bc5f9149f7b0c1bbf2a94","tid":839150,"uid":28624,"like":525,"dislike":1,"score":524,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:06:25.000Z","msg":"力加都有文化過下等既支那人"},{"pid":"93125a268a8355c4965047b45ef316eca80efadc","tid":839150,"uid":62384,"like":139,"dislike":1,"score":138,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:09:18.000Z","msg":"做乜俾個鏟佢<br />\n要佢用手執嘛"},{"pid":"f6cfea5ad76740855c4ce55a704d45d7bbc8b795","tid":839150,"uid":37586,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:09:25.000Z","msg":"狗改不了屙屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728a57ca6426048caaa86327744847b3225f3542","tid":839150,"uid":62011,"like":174,"dislike":2,"score":172,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:09:29.000Z","msg":"nigga&gt;&gt;&gt;狗&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;支國人"},{"pid":"9cb32d15e4a227aa61fe26d5ed3cabb33af37bfd","tid":839150,"uid":62384,"like":799,"dislike":5,"score":794,"quote":{"pid":"7606f958423cbf96d49bc5f9149f7b0c1bbf2a94","tid":839150,"uid":28624,"like":525,"dislike":1,"score":524,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:06:25.000Z","msg":"力加都有文化過下等既支那人"},"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:25:45.000Z","msg":"講起有次我去公廁痾尿見到<br />\n黑鬼怒屌阿叔<br />\n<br />\n我入到廁所聽到有人嘈<br />\n一個黑鬼同個阿叔係度嘈<br />\n<br />\n黑鬼成個泰臣咁<br />\n阿叔就5，60歲短褲背心拖鞋<br />\n<br />\n我一路痾一路聽<br />\n係個阿叔痾完屎唔沖廁<br />\n黑鬼捉住佢要佢沖廁先好走<br />\n<br />\n阿叔不斷係咪屌你老母關你撚寧<br />\n黑鬼就唔撚俾佢走<br />\n<br />\n我問黑鬼要唔要幫佢翻譯<br />\n黑鬼點頭<br />\n<br />\n我連粗口都幫佢翻譯埋<br />\n慶到黑鬼係咁叫佢把口乾淨d<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n阿叔就屌我多鳩事<br />\n仲話中國人唔幫中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母啦<br />\n我唔係中國人<br />\n我係香港人<br />\n<br />\n越來越多人出入廁所<br />\n有d停係度睇嘢<br />\n又幫口屌阿叔<br />\n阿叔淨係識關你撚事咩<br />\n痾完就走啦<br />\n<br />\n最後都係要沖廁黑鬼先放佢走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n臨走仲屌鳩我話我死漢奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a16e9ee033cd1c53fc2ec4d1f644b605c77169","tid":839150,"uid":17859,"like":288,"dislike":1,"score":287,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:28:39.000Z","msg":"欢迎来到迦纳<br />\n我们不在花园裡拉屎"},{"pid":"5612e844ee4bdb8e97fb3f89088267242b46b618","tid":839150,"uid":22701,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:38:17.000Z","msg":"迦納人都有文化過支那豬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65f0e7af5e9bde87b4e92f2cf8f9dd376416696","tid":839150,"uid":24853,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:50:25.000Z","msg":"真係要推比支那狗睇"},{"pid":"1b11ce4d44e0e1a0601ecf96dac92dafad5633f3","tid":839150,"uid":144378,"like":3,"dislike":53,"score":-50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"