moji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T09:51:33.000Z","msg":"沖個廁都咁多爹 搞到自己咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96984612cc64a36f87c4360d432302c984a0af5d","tid":839150,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e33958e351a703c544dd5cc5b226c37aa639078","tid":839150,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7606f958423cbf96d49bc5f9149f7b0c1bbf2a94","tid":839150,"uid":28624,"like":525,"dislike":1,"score":524,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:06:25.000Z","msg":"力加都有文化過下等既支那人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:44:13.000Z","msg":"蠢=/=冇文化冇良知<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T09:56:53.000Z","msg":"喺網上Nigger前Nigger後嘅連登仔，去到現實見到真黑人就唔敢咁吠架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5745e8427aa5e17342e6018b3fe79ac29c92561","tid":839150,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T09:59:50.000Z","msg":"以為會捉住條友，質返舊屎入屎忽窿"},{"pid":"0b50807dcfba93c9845193b05a0399dd2440f27b","tid":839150,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96984612cc64a36f87c4360d432302c984a0af5d","tid":839150,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e33958e351a703c544dd5cc5b226c37aa639078","tid":839150,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7606f958423cbf96d49bc5f9149f7b0c1bbf2a94","tid":839150,"uid":28624,"like":525,"dislike":1,"score":524,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:06:25.000Z","msg":"力加都有文化過下等既支那人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:44:13.000Z","msg":"蠢=/=冇文化冇良知<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T09:56:53.000Z","msg":"喺網上Nigger前Nigger後嘅連登仔，去到現實見到真黑人就唔敢咁吠架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T10:43:47.000Z","msg":"同佢地講 yo what's up my nigger 會無事<br />\n外國好平常，係正常溝通嚟，有少少開玩笑嘅意味"},{"pid":"63bf07b973